<title>USA: MDL loses almost 50 pct after Q2 forecast.</title>
<headline>MDL loses almost 50 pct after Q2 forecast.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1996-10-11</dateline>
<text>
<p>MDL Information Systems Inc shares were pummelled in early trading Friday after the company said following the market close on Thursday that it expected substantially lower second quarter earnings.</p>
<p>The stock fell 14-5/8, or 48 percent, to 15-5/8 in early trading.</p>
<p>MDL forecast second-quarter earnings per share in a range of $0.10-$0.12, compared with $0.19 in the year-ago period. It said revenues for the period should rise to $15 million to $16 million, up from $14 million in the year-ago period.</p>
</text>
